import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Grid,
  IconButton,
  Link,
  makeStyles,
  Typography,
} from "@material-ui/core";
import { Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, Twitter } from "@material-ui/icons";
import React from "react";

const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
  footer: {
    backgroundColor: theme.palette.grey[900],
    color: theme.palette.common.white,
    padding: theme.spacing(6, 0),
  },
  link: {
    color: theme.palette.common.white,
    "&:hover": {
      color: theme.palette.secondary.main,
    },
  },
}));

const Footer = () => {
  const classes = useStyles();

  return (
    <Box component="footer" className={classes.footer}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              About 7Bus
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2">
              We provide comfortable and reliable bus services for all your
              travel needs.
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Quick Links
            </Typography>
            <Box>
              <Link href="#" className={classes.link}>
                Home
              </Link>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Link href="#" className={classes.link}>
                About Us
              </Link>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Link href="#" className={classes.link}>
                Services
              </Link>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Link href="#" className={classes.link}>
                Contact
              </Link>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Contact Us
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2">123 Bus Street, City Name</Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2">Email: info@7bus.com</Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2">Phone: +91 1234567890</Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={3}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Follow Us
            </Typography>
            <IconButton className={classes.link}>
              <Facebook />
            </IconButton>
            <IconButton className={classes.link}>
              <Twitter />
            </IconButton>
            <IconButton className={classes.link}>
              <Instagram />
            </IconButton>
            <IconButton className={classes.link}>
              <LinkedIn />
            </IconButton>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Box mt={5}>
          <Typography variant="body2" align="center">
            © 2024 7Bus. All rights reserved.
          </Typography>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Footer;
